text: Tweet #2: Thank you SO MUCH for your kindness! I'm getting many Qs, so answering them here for efficiency. People are asking what criteria they need to meet to donate plasma & which patients with #COVID19 can get plasma & how. See here: https://t.co/Yd7YIBEBmT. https://t.co/5sNKPLRqkf
